307 453 610 614 945 1409 1678 1891 2344 2818 <char style="it">Byz</char> [L P] <char style="it">Lect</char> (<char style="it">l</char> 751 <char style="it">omit</char> </char><char style="fk" closed="false">με</char><char style="ft" closed="false">) it<char style="add">ar, c, d, dem, e, gig, p, ph, ro, w</char> vg syr<char style="add">p, h</char> cop<char style="add">bo</char> Chrysostom; Quodvultdeus<char style="add">1/2</char> BJ BTI</char></note> ὑπονοεῖτε εἶναι; οὐκ εἰμὶ ἐγώ· ἀλλ᾽ ἰδοὺ ἔρχεται μετ᾽ ἐμὲ οὗ οὐκ εἰμὶ ἄξιος τὸ ὑπόδημα τῶν ποδῶν λῦσαι.</para>
  <para style="p">
