        <ref loc="ACT 13:16">Ac 13.16</ref>
      </char>
    </note>Ἄνδρες ἀδελφοί, υἱοὶ γένους Ἀβραὰμ καὶ οἱ ἐν ὑμῖν φοβούμενοι τὸν θεόν, ἡμῖν<note caller="6" style="f"><char style="fr" closed="false">13.26 </char><char style="ft" closed="false">{B} </char><char style="fk" closed="false">ἡμῖν </char><char style="ft" closed="false">𝔓<char style="add">74</char> ℵ A B D Ψ 33 81 614 2344<char style="add">vid</char> it<char style="add">d, sin</char> syr<char style="add">h<char style="add">mg</char></char> cop<char style="add">sa, meg</char> ⫽ </char><char style="fk" closed="false">ὑμῖν </char><char style="ft" closed="false">𝔓<char style="add">45</char> C E 181 307 453 610 945 1175 1409 1678 1739 1881 2818 <char style="it">Byz</char> [L P] <char style="it">Lect</char> it<char style="add">ar, c, dem, e, gig, p, ph, ro, t, w</char> vg syr<char style="add">p, h</char> cop<char style="add">bo</char> arm eth geo slav Chrysostom BJ</char></note> ὁ λόγος τῆς σωτηρίας ταύτης ἐξαπεστάλη. <verse number="27" style="v" /><note caller="*" style="x"><char style="xo" closed="false">13.27 </char><char style="xt" closed="false"><ref loc="ACT 3:17">Ac 3.17</ref></char></note>οἱ γὰρ κατοικοῦντες ἐν Ἰερουσαλὴμ καὶ οἱ ἄρχοντες αὐτῶν τοῦτον ἀγνοήσαντες καὶ τὰς φωνὰς τῶν προφητῶν τὰς κατὰ πᾶν σάββατον ἀναγινωσκομένας κρίναντες<note caller="7" style="f"><char style="fr" closed="false">13.27 </char><char style="ft" closed="false">{A} </char><char style="fk" closed="false">τοῦτον ἀγνοήσαντες καὶ τὰς φωνὰς … κρίναντες </char><char style="ft" closed="false">𝔓<char style="add">45, 74</char> ℵ A B C (D<char style="add">2</char> </char><char style="fk" closed="false">ἀγνοοῦντες</char><char style="ft" closed="false">) Ψ 33 81 181 307 453 610 614 945 1175 1409 1678 1739 1891 2344 2818 <char style="it">Byz</char> [L P] <char style="it">Lect</char> (<char style="it">l</char> 1364 <char style="it">l</char> 1365 <char style="it">l</char> 1441 </char><char style="fk" closed="false">κρίνοντες</char><char style="ft" closed="false">) it<char style="add">(ar), c, dem, gig, p, ph, ro, sin, t, w</char> vg syr<char style="add">h</char> (cop<char style="add">sa, bo, meg</char>) arm geo slav Chrysostom ⫽ </char><char style="fk" closed="false">τοῦτον ἀγνοήσαντες καὶ τὰς γραφὰς … κρίναντες </char><char style="ft" closed="false">E it<char style="add">e</char> syr<char style="add">p</char> ⫽ </char><char style="fk" closed="false">μὴ συνιέντες τὰς γραφὰς … καὶ κρίναντες </char><char style="ft" closed="false">D<char style="add">*vid</char> it<char style="add">d</char> (eth) BJ</char></note> ἐπλήρωσαν, <verse number="28" style="v" /><note caller="*" style="x"><char style="xo" closed="false">13.28 </char><char style="xq" closed="false">μηδεμίαν … εὑρόντες </char><char style="xt" closed="false"><ref loc="MAT 26:60">Mt 26.60</ref>; <ref loc="MRK 14:55">Mk 14.55</ref>, <ref loc="MRK 14:56">56</ref>, <ref loc="MRK 14:59">59</ref>; <ref loc="MRK 15:14">15.14</ref>; <ref loc="LUK 23:4">Lk 23.4</ref>, <ref loc="LUK 23:14">14</ref>, <ref loc="LUK 23:15">15</ref>, <ref loc="LUK 23:22">22</ref>; <ref loc="JHN 18:38">Jn 18.38</ref>; <ref loc="JHN 19:4">19.4</ref>, <ref loc="JHN 19:6">6</ref> </char><char style="xq" closed="false">ᾐτήσαντο … αὐτόν </char><char style="xt" closed="false"><ref loc="MAT 27:22-23">Mt 27.22‑23</ref>; <ref loc="MRK 15:13-14">Mk 15.13‑14</ref>; <ref loc="LUK 23:21">Lk 23.21</ref>, <ref loc="LUK 23:23">23</ref>; <ref loc="JHN 19:6">Jn 19.6</ref>, <ref loc="JHN 19:7">7</ref>, <ref loc="JHN 19:15">15</ref></char></note>καὶ μηδεμίαν αἰτίαν θανάτου εὑρόντες ᾐτήσαντο Πιλᾶτον ἀναιρεθῆναι αὐτόν. <verse number="29" style="v" /><note caller="*" style="x"><char style="xo" closed="false">13.29 </char><char style="xq" closed="false">καθελόντες … μνημεῖον </char><char style="xt" closed="false"><ref loc="MAT 27:59-60">Mt 27.59‑60</ref>; <ref loc="MRK 15:46">Mk 15.46</ref>; <ref loc="LUK 23:53">Lk 23.53</ref>; <ref loc="JHN 19:38">Jn 19.38</ref>, <ref loc="JHN 19:41-42">41‑42</ref></char></note>ὡς δὲ ἐτέλεσαν πάντα τὰ περὶ αὐτοῦ γεγραμμένα, καθελόντες ἀπὸ τοῦ ξύλου ἔθηκαν εἰς μνημεῖον. <verse number="30" style="v" /><note caller="*" style="x"><char style="xo" closed="false">13.30 </char><char style="xq" closed="false">ὁ δὲ … νεκρῶν </char><char style="xt" closed="false"><ref loc="ACT 2:24">Ac 2.24</ref>, <ref loc="ACT 2:32">32</ref>; <ref loc="ACT 3:15">3.15</ref>; <ref loc="ACT 4:10">4.10</ref>; <ref loc="ACT 5:30">5.30</ref>; <ref loc="ACT 10:40">10.40</ref>; <ref loc="ACT 17:31">17.31</ref></char></note>ὁ δὲ θεὸς ἤγειρεν αὐτὸν ἐκ νεκρῶν, <verse number="31" style="v" /><note caller="*" style="x"><char style="xo" closed="false">13.31 </char><char style="xq" closed="false">ὃς ὤφθη … εἰς Ἰερουσαλήμ </char><char style="xt" closed="false"><ref loc="ACT 1:3">Ac 1.3</ref> </char><char style="xq" closed="false">οἵτινες … μάρτυρες αὐτοῦ </char><char style="xt" closed="false"><ref loc="LUK 24:48">Lk 24.48</ref>; <ref loc="ACT 1:8">Ac 1.8</ref>; <ref loc="ACT 2:32">2.32</ref>; <ref loc="ACT 3:15">3.15</ref>; <ref loc="ACT 5:32">5.32</ref>; <ref loc="ACT 10:39">10.39</ref>, <ref loc="ACT 10:41">41</ref></char></note>ὃς ὤφθη ἐπὶ ἡμέρας πλείους τοῖς συναναβᾶσιν αὐτῷ ἀπὸ τῆς Γαλιλαίας εἰς Ἰερουσαλήμ, οἵτινες [νῦν] εἰσιν μάρτυρες αὐτοῦ πρὸς τὸν λαόν. <verse number="32" style="v" /><note caller="*" style="x"><char style="xo" closed="false">13.32‑33 </char><char style="xq" closed="false">ἡμεῖς … Ἰησοῦν </char><char style="xt" closed="false"><ref loc="ACT 13:23">Ac 13.23</ref></char></note>καὶ ἡμεῖς ὑμᾶς εὐαγγελιζόμεθα τὴν πρὸς τοὺς πατέρας ἐπαγγελίαν γενομένην, <verse number="33" style="v" /><note caller="*" style="x"><char style="xo" closed="false">13.33 </char><char style="xq" closed="false">Υἱός … σε </char><char style="xt" closed="false"><ref loc="PSA 2:7">Ps 2.7</ref> (<ref loc="HEB 1:5">He 1.5</ref>; <ref loc="HEB 5:5">5.5</ref>)</char></note>ὅτι ταύτην ὁ θεὸς ἐκπεπλήρωκεν τοῖς τέκνοις [αὐτῶν] ἡμῖν<note caller="8" style="f"><char style="fr" closed="false">13.33 </char><char style="ft" closed="false">{C} </char><ch