  <para style="q1">
    <char style="qt">Υἱός μου εἶ σύ,</char></para>
  <para style="q2">
    <char style="qt">ἐγὼ σήμερον γεγέννηκά σε.</char></para>
  <para style="m">
    <verse number="34" style="v" />
    <note caller="*" style="x">
      <char style="xo" closed="false">13.34 </char>
      <char style="xq" closed="false">Δώσω … πιστά </char>
      <char style="xt" closed="false">
        <ref loc="ISA 55:3">Is 55.3</ref> <char style="sc">lxx</char></char>
    </note>ὅτι δὲ ἀνέστησεν αὐτὸν ἐκ νεκρῶν μηκέτι μέλλοντα ὑποστρέφειν εἰς διαφθοράν, οὕτως εἴρηκεν ὅτι</para>
  <para style="q1">Δώσω <char style="qt">ὑμῖν τὰ ὅσια Δαυὶδ τὰ πιστά.</char></para>
  <para style="m">
    <verse number="35" style="v" />
    <note caller="*" style="x">
      <char style="xo" closed="false">13.35 </char>
      <char style="xq" closed="false">Οὐ … διαφθοράν </char>
      <char style="xt" closed="false">
        <ref loc="PSA 16:10">Ps 16.10</ref> <char style="sc">lxx</char></char>
    </note>διότι καὶ ἐν ἑτέρῳ λέγει,</para>
  <para style="q1">
    <char style="qt">Οὐ δώσεις τὸν ὅσιόν σου ἰδεῖν διαφθοράν.</char></para>
  <para style="m">
    <verse number="36" style="v" />
    <note caller="*" style="x">
      <char style="xo" closed="false">13.36 </char>
      <char style="xq" closed="false">Δαυὶδ … αὐτοῦ </char>
      <char style="xt" closed="false">
        <ref loc="1KI 2:10">1 Kgs 2.10</ref>; <ref loc="ACT 2:29">Ac 2.29</ref> </char>
      <char style="xq" closed="false">προσετέθη … αὐτοῦ </char>
      <char style="xt" closed="false">
        <ref loc="JDG 2:10">Jdg 2.10</ref>
      </char>
    </note>Δαυὶδ μὲν γὰρ ἰδίᾳ γενεᾷ ὑπηρετήσας τῇ τοῦ θεοῦ βουλῇ ἐκοιμήθη καὶ προσετέθη πρὸς τοὺς πατέρας αὐτοῦ καὶ εἶδεν διαφθοράν· <verse number="37" style="v" />ὃν δὲ ὁ θεὸς ἤγειρεν, οὐκ εἶδεν διαφθοράν. <verse number="38" style="v" /><note caller="*" style="x"><char style="xo" closed="false">13.38 </char><char style="xq" closed="false">διὰ … καταγγέλλεται </char><char style="xt" closed="false"><ref loc="ACT 10:43">Ac 10.43</ref> </char><char style="xq" closed="false">ἀπὸ … δικαιωθῆναι </char><char style="xt" closed="false"><ref loc="HEB 9:9">He 9.9</ref></char></note>γνωστὸν οὖν ἔστω ὑμῖν, ἄνδρες ἀδελφοί, ὅτι διὰ τούτου ὑμῖν ἄφεσις ἁμαρτιῶν καταγγέλλεται, [καὶ] ἀπὸ πάντων ὧν οὐκ ἠδυνήθητε ἐν νόμῳ Μωϋσέως δικαιωθῆναι, <verse number="39" style="v" /><note caller="*" style="x"><char style="xo" closed="false">13.39 </char><char style="xq" closed="false">ἐν … δικαιοῦται </char><char style="xt" closed="false"><ref loc="ROM 4:25">Ro 4.25</ref>; <ref loc="ROM 6:7">6.7</ref>; <ref loc="ROM 10:4">10.4</ref></char></note>ἐν τούτῳ πᾶς ὁ πιστεύων δικαιοῦται. <verse number="40" style="v" />βλέπετε οὖν μὴ ἐπέλθῃ<note caller="10" style="f"><char style="fr" closed="false">13.40 </char><char style="ft" closed="false">{B} </char><char style="fk" closed="false">ἐπέλθῃ </char><char style="ft" closed="false">𝔓<char style="add">74</char> ℵ<char style="add">2</char> (ℵ* </char><char style="fk" closed="false">ἀπέλθῃ</char><char style="ft" closed="false">) B D 33 307 453 610 1678 2344 2818 it<char style="add">d</char> vg<char style="add">st</char> ⫽ </char><char style="fk" closed="false">ἐπέλθῃ ἐφ᾽ ὑμᾶς </char><char style="ft" closed="false">A C E Ψ 097 81 181 (614 εἰς ὑμᾶς <char style="it">after</char> προφήταις) 945 1175 1409 1739 1891 <char style="it">Byz</char> [L P] <char style="it">l</char> 1178 it<char style="add">ar, c, dem, e, gig, p, ph, ro, w</char> vg<char style="add">cl, ww</char> syr<char style="add">p, h</char> cop<char style="add">sa, bo, meg</char> arm eth geo slav Basil Chrysostom GNB NRSV? EU? TOB? BTI DHH?</char></note> τὸ εἰρημένον ἐν τοῖς προφήταις,</para>
  <para style="q1">
    <verse number="41" style="v" />
    <note caller="*" style="x">
      <char style="xo" closed="false">13.41 </char>
      <char style="xt" closed="false">
        <ref loc="HAB 1:5">Hab 1.5</ref> <char style="sc">lxx</char></char>
    </note>
    <char style="qt">Ἴδετε, οἱ καταφρονηταί,</char></para>
  <para style="q2">
    <char style="qt">καὶ θαυμάσατε καὶ ἀφανίσθητε,</char></para>
  <para style="q1">
    <char style="qt">ὅτι ἔργον ἐργάζομαι ἐγὼ ἐν ταῖς ἡμέραις ὑμῶν,</char></para>
  <para style="q2">ἔργον <char style="qt">ὃ οὐ μὴ πιστεύσητε ἐάν τις ἐκδιηγῆται ὑμῖν.</char></para>
  <para style="p">
    <verse number="42" style="v" />Ἐξιόντων δὲ αὐτῶν<note caller="11" style="f"><char style="fr" closed="false">13.42 </char><char style="ft" closed="false">{A} </char><char style="fk" closed="false">αὐτῶν </char><char style="ft" closed="false">𝔓<char style="add">74</char> ℵ A B C D E Ψ 097 81 181 307 453 610 614 945 1175 1678 1739 1891 2344 2818 <char style="it">l</char> 1178<char style="add">1/2</char> it<char style="add">ar, c, d, dem, e, gig, p, ph, ro, w</char> vg syr<char style="add">(p), h</char> cop<char style="add">sa, bo, meg</char> arm slav<char style="add">ms</char> Chrysostom<char style="add">lem</char> ⫽ </char><char style="fk" closed="false">ἐκ τῆς συναγωγῆς τῶν Ἰουδαίων </char><char style="ft" closed="false"><char style="it">Byz</char><char style="add">pt</char> [P] ⫽ </char><char style="fk" closed="false">αὐτῶν ἐκ τῆς συναγωγῆς τῶν Ἰουδαίων </char><char style="ft" closed="false">1409 <char style="it">Byz</char><char style="add">pt</char> [L] <char style="it">l</char> 1178<char style="add">1/2</char> slav<char style="add">ms</char> (NIV) (BTI) (DHH)</char></note> παρεκάλουν εἰς τὸ μεταξὺ σάββατον<note caller="12" style="f"><char style="fr" closed="false">13.42 </char><char style="ft" closed="false">{B} </char><char style="fk" closed="false">παρεκάλουν εἰς τὸ μεταξὺ σάββατον </char><char style="ft" closed="false">𝔓<char style="add">74</char> ℵ A C Ψ 097 33 (307 453 610 1678 2818 </char><char style="fk" closed="false">παρεκάλουν </char><char style="ft" closed="false"><char style="it">after</char> </char><char style="fk" closed="false">σάββατον</char><char style="ft" closed="false">) 81 181 614 945 1175 1739 1891 2344 <char style="it">l</char> 1178<char style="add">1/2</char> it<char style="add">ar, c, d, dem, gig, p, ph, ro, w</char> vg syr<char style="add">p, h</char> cop<char style="add">sa, meg</char> arm (eth) slav<char style="add">ms</char> Chrysostom<char style="add">lem</char> ⫽ </char><char style="fk" closed="false">παρεκάλουν τὰ ἔθνη εἰς τὸ με